cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision techniques for detecting flying objects from a moving camera. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) since it deals with detecting UAVs. The use of machine learning algorithms for object detection makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also involves statistical learning (cs.LG) since it uses machine learning algorithms. Finally, the paper involves multimedia (cs.MM) since it deals with video analysis.
